text: Alexander Wennberg (born 22 September 1994) is a Swedish professional ice hockey player. He currently plays for the Seattle Kraken of the National Hockey League (NHL). He used to play for the Columbus Blue Jackets and Florida Panthers. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Seattle Kraken players Category:Columbus Blue Jackets players Category:Florida Panthers players Category:Swedish ice hockey centres
